    "created_at": "2015-09-01T14:38:53Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-09-01T15:00:13Z",
    "body": "The second issue with scaling on Windows is still an issue in 0.31.1.\n\nEDIT: Possibly related to that issue; on scaled desktops, window.outerHeight / outerWidth are set incorrectly. They appear to be scaled down based on the windows desktop scale ratio. So if you have desktop scaling set to 200%, a window 800px wide will have a outerWidth of 400.\n"
